author: Nick Romano
title: LEGO Batman, Fifty Shades Darker get mashup on Jimmy Kimmel
text:
Email 
The relationship between Batman and the Joker gets a slight S&M edge in Jimmy Kimmel’s mashup video featuring the two big movie releases this weekend: The LEGO Batman Movie and Fifty Shades Darker . 
The host of Jimmy Kimmel Live showed his Thursday night audience what would happen if he layered dialogue from the raunchy romance over footage of the mini Dark Knight. The result was “Fifty Shades Darker Knight,” in which Batman talks about giving the Joker a spanking. 
Bruce Wayne (voiced by Will Arnett) and Christian Grey (Jamie Dornan) do have some things in common: They are both tortured billionaires needing some connection, and both do have whips and chains, although Bats uses them to lock up criminals and Christian, well, you get the idea. 
The LEGO Batman Movie and Fifty Shades Darker are out now in theaters. Watch Kimmel’s mashup video above. Show Full Article
